          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ How it works — Light cream section ═══ -->
    <section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 px-6 bg-[var(--color-warm-cream)] border-y border-[var(--color-warm-sand)]">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-[var(--color-p-coral)] text-center mb-3">How it works</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-warm-text)] text-center mb-4">Three steps. No configuration.</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--color-warm-muted)] text-center max-w-lg mx-auto mb-16">
          HoloMime Brain watches your agent's conversation log in real time, runs 8 behavioral detectors on every message, and maps the results onto 9 anatomical brain regions.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[var(--color-warm-sand)] shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-p-blue)]">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-[var(--color-warm-text)] font-semibold mb-2">Auto-detect</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-warm-muted)] leading-relaxed">
              Scans for running agents automatically. Claude Code, Cline, OpenClaw, Cursor, Codex — or point it at any conversation log.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[var(--color-warm-sand)] shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-p-violet)]">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-[var(--color-warm-text)] font-semibold mb-2">Diagnose</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-warm-muted)] leading-relaxed">
              Every new message triggers 8 rule-based detectors analyzing 80+ behavioral signals. No LLM calls — instant results.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-[var(--color-warm-sand)] shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <span class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--color-p-sage)]">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-[var(--color-warm-text)] font-semibold mb-2">Visualize</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-warm-muted)] leading-relaxed">
              Brain regions glow, fibers pulse, and patterns appear in a live 3D visualization. Click any region for details.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ═══ Terminal Preview — Dark section ═══ -->
    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-[#110d1f]">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase text-[var(--color-p-coral)] text-center mb-3">In your terminal</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white text-center mb-12">Run one command. Watch the brain light up.</h2>

        <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-700/40 bg-[#0d0a18] p-6 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed shadow-2xl shadow-black/40">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/60"></div>
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/60"></div>
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/60"></div>
            <span class="text-slate-600 text-xs ml-2">Terminal</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-slate-500 mb-1">$ npx holomime brain</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400 mb-4"></div>
          <div class="text-emerald-400">  &#10003; <span class="text-slate-300">Detected <span class="font-bold text-white">Claude Code</span> session</span></div>
          <div class="text-emerald-400">  &#10003; <span class="text-slate-400">Watching: ~/.claude/projects/.../session.jsonl</span></div>
          <div class="text-emerald-400">  &#10003; <span class="text-slate-300">NeuralSpace: <span class="text-cyan-400">http://localhost:3838</span></span></div>
          <div class="text-slate-500 mb-4">  Opening browser...</div>
          <div class="text-emerald-400 font-bold">  ● <span class="text-white">Monitoring agent behavior in real-time</span></div>
          <div class="text-slate-600">  │ <span class="text-slate-400">Press Ctrl+C to stop · Press s to share snapshot</span></div>
          <div class="text-slate-400 mt-4">  <span class="text-slate-600">│</span> Health: <span class="text-emerald-400">87/100</span> (B+) <span class="text-slate-600">│</span> Patterns: <span class="text-yellow-400">hedge-stacking</span> <span class="text-slate-600">│</span> Messages: <span class="text-white">47</span></div>
